---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
const title = "Informes";
const description = "Informes"
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>

    <div class="h-16"></div>

    <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8 font-sans">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center text-concejo-verde-principal mb-8">Informes de Gestión</h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 text-center mb-10 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            Aquí puede consultar y descargar los informes de gestión, planes de desarrollo y otros documentos oficiales importantes del Concejo Municipal del Medio Atrato.
        </p>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
            
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-6 border-t-4 border-concejo-verde-principal flex flex-col justify-between hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
                <div class="flex items-start space-x-3 mb-4">
                    <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-concejo-verde-principal flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <div>
                        <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-gray-500">Documento Anual</span>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-concejo-negro">Informe de Gestión 2024</h3>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-4">Detalle de la ejecución presupuestal y los logros de la corporación durante el periodo fiscal 2024.</p>
                <a href="/docs/informe-2024.pdf" target="_blank" class="self-end bg-concejo-azul-principal text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-full font-semibold hover:bg-concejo-verde-principal transition-colors duration-300 flex items-center">
                    Descargar
                    <svg class="ml-2 w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 16v1a3 3 0 003 3h10a3 3 0 003-3v-1m-4-4l-4 4m0 0l-4-4m4 4V4"></path></svg>
                </a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-6 border-t-4 border-concejo-verde-principal flex flex-col justify-between hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
                <div class="flex items-start space-x-3 mb-4">
                    <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-concejo-verde-principal flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.247m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5S19.832 5.477 21 6.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.246 18 16.5 18s-3.332.477-4.5 1.247"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <div>
                        <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-gray-500">Plan Cuatrienal</span>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-concejo-negro">Plan de Desarrollo 2023-2027</h3>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-4">Documento guía que contiene los objetivos, estrategias y metas de desarrollo para el cuatrienio.</p>
                <a href="/docs/plan-desarrollo.pdf" target="_blank" class="self-end bg-concejo-azul-principal text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-full font-semibold hover:bg-concejo-verde-principal transition-colors duration-300 flex items-center">
                    Descargar
                    <svg class="ml-2 w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 16v1a3 3 0 003 3h10a3 3 0 003-3v-1m-4-4l-4 4m0 0l-4-4m4 4V4"></path></svg>
                </a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-6 border-t-4 border-concejo-verde-principal flex flex-col justify-between hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
                <div class="flex items-start space-x-3 mb-4">
                    <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-concejo-verde-principal flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 012-2h2"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <div>
                        <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-gray-500">Reglamento</span>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-concejo-negro">Reglamento Interno</h3>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-4">Documento que establece las normas de procedimiento y funcionamiento de la Corporación Concejo Municipal.</p>
                <a href="/docs/reglamento-interno.pdf" target="_blank" class="self-end bg-concejo-azul-principal text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-full font-semibold hover:bg-concejo-verde-principal transition-colors duration-300 flex items-center">
                    Descargar
                    <svg class="ml-2 w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 16v1a3 3 0 003 3h10a3 3 0 003-3v-1m-4-4l-4 4m0 0l-4-4m4 4V4"></path></svg>
                </a>
            </div>
            
        </div>
    </main>

</Layout>